atched by carrier'=>'Odoslaná dopravcom','Delivered'=>'Doručené','Refund'=>'Vrátenie peňazí','Returned to the consignor'=>'Vrátená odosielateľovi','Shipment cancelled'=>'Zásielka zrušená','The shipment has been received and is on its way to the depot'=>'Zásielka bola prijatá a je na ceste do depa','Reverse packet has been accepted at our branch'=>'Reverzný balík bol prijatý na našej pobočke','Packeta Home made unsuccessful delivery attempt of packet'=>'Packeta Home vykonala neúspešný pokus o doručenie balíka','Packeta Home delivery attempt of packet end in rejected by recipient response'=>'Packeta Home pokus o doručenie balíka skončil odmietnutím zo strany príjemcu','Packet rejected by recipient (non HD rejection)'=>'Paket odmietnutý príjemcom (odmietnutie bez HD)','Packeta Home delivery made unsuccessful delivery attempt of packet and there was no branch for redirection nearby.'=>'Packeta Home delivery uskutočnila neúspešný pokus o doručenie balíka a v blízkosti nebola žiadna pobočka, kde by bolo možné balík presmerovať.','Storage time expired and packet will be returned.'=>'Doba skladovania uplynula a balík bude vrátený.','Packet was cancelled but it was consigned later on. Packet will be returned.'=>'Balík bol zrušený, ale neskôr bol odoslaný. Balík bude vrátený.','Packet does not meet the shipping conditions (overlimit) and will be returned.'=>'Balík nespĺňa podmienky prepravy (prekročenie limitu) a bude vrátený.','Unsuccessful delivery attempt of packet into Z-BOX.'=>'Neúspešný pokus o doručenie paketu do Z-BOX.','Last delivery attempt to the box has been made. A change in the delivery method will be required.'=>'Bol vykonaný posledný pokus o doručenie do schránky. Bude potrebné zmeniť spôsob doručenia.','First delivery attempt made by external carrier.'=>'Prvý pokus o doručenie vykonaný externým prepravcom.','Packet is currently being reviewed.'=>'Balík je momentálne v procese kontroly.','Review of the packet has been completed.'=>'Prehľad balíka bol dokončený